A page from the technical specification of deployed drones
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Bot


The bot is the slowest unit in the SUF arsenal. It is mostly deployed for patrolling dense urban or forest areas. 
The bot unit is cheap but neither flexible nor strong. If caught by surprise, it can be destroyed by a single handgun shot.


Armor type: Light

Weapon type: Light gun

Damage: 1

Chaussie type: Legs (Can cross plain and rough terrain, no water)

Max Life: 15

Speed factor: 1


Weaknesses: 


Its light armor makes the bots vulnerable against handguns. A shot from behind can completely destoy the unit. 